.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, russian, malaysian, chinese, spanish, turkish, egyptian
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, mouse, frog, lizard, bird, chinchilla
 1. the spanish is on the left of the nigerian##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is the egyptian##1
 4. the malaysian is on the left of the turkish##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the chinese is the owner of the frog##1
 7. the nigerian is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the chinchilla and the chinese##2
 9. the nigerian is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the russian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | spanish | nigerian | russian   | chinese | malaysian | turkish |
| Pet           | lizard | bird     | snake     | mouse | frog   | hedgehog   | chinchilla    |

