.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, almond-milk, milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, mirinda
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, argentine, indian, thai, canadian, turkish
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the argentine##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the thai##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the indian##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the thai##1
 5. the indonesian is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the indian is between the person drinking almond-milk and the canadian##2
 7. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
 8. the indian is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is the italian##1
10. the indonesian is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | hot-chocolate  | milk  | coffee  | mirinda      | soy-milk       | 7up |
| Nationality   | thai | indian | canadian | turkish | indonesian | argentine | italian  |

