.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, blues, reggae, jazz, country, trance, indie
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, quad-bike, taxi, bus, jet-ski, airplane
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the bus is the fan of blues##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the fan of indie and the fan of electronic##2
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the subway is the fan of jazz##1
9. the fan of country is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | country | electronic | reggae | indie      | blues      | trance |
| Transport     | subway | jet-ski | airplane       | snowmobile | quad-bike | bus | taxi |

