.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker, accountant, lawyer, fisherman, teacher, dancer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, volleyball, biathlon, weightlifting, tennis, water-polo, surfing
1. the accountant is on the left of the dancer##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the fisherman##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the teacher is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is tennis and the designer##2
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
8. the teacher is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | fisherman | designer | lawyer | teacher | dressmaker | accountant     | dancer |
| Sport   | biathlon   | weightlifting    | surfing    | tennis      | volleyball  | rugby | water-polo |

