.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, mirinda, tea, water, soy-milk, sprite
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, snowboarding, sailing, skateboarding, soccer, lacrosse, golf
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is golf##2
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking water##2
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | 7up | juice    | tea | mirinda   | soy-milk | sprite    | water |
| Sport      | skateboarding | water-polo | golf    | snowboarding | soccer    | sailing | lacrosse  |

