.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, almond-milk, coffee, 7up, iced-tea, sprite
The people have 7 different jobs:  scientist, designer, videographer, pilot, firefighter, writer, coach
 1. the firefighter is on the left of the pilot##1
 2. the scientist is on the left of the videographer##1
 3. the writer is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the firefighter is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking sprite##2
 7. the designer is on the right of the writer##1
 8. the scientist is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking soy-milk##2
11. the firefighter is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | 7up   | soy-milk         | tea     | sprite              | iced-tea    | coffee     |
| Job        | writer | designer | firefighter | pilot | coach | scientist | videographer |

