.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, epic, western, time-travel, scientific, crime, family
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, subway, boat, van, jet-ski, car, snowmobile
1. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the jet-ski##2
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | time-travel     | crime | scientific | western | family  | drama |
| Transport     | boat | van | jet-ski   | roller     | snowmobile    | subway | car   |

