.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, almond-milk, juice, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, sudoku, drawing, card-games, chess, fishing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | water  | iced-tea       | sprite         | hot-chocolate         | juice   | almond-milk        | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | woodworking | drawing | baking | chess | sudoku | fishing | card-games  |

