4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | fishing | collecting       | chess    | camping | filmmaking | board-games     | dancing       |
| Sport   | handball    | rugby | surfing | climbing        | swimming | baseball | cricket |

