The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, romance, drama, action, crime, comedy, scientific
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, trance, classical, metal, funk, gospel, soul
 1. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of soul##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching action movies and the fan of dubstep##2
 4. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching crime movies##2
 5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the fan of metal is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | superhero | romance  | crime   | comedy | scientific | drama |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | soul       | dubstep | classical | gospel  | trance   | funk   |

