 3. the person eating peas is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating blueberry##2
 5. the person eating potato is the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person eating almond-milkmelon is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person eating apricot##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
10. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | juice       | coffee | soy-milk      | tea | almond-milk       | 7up | sprite |
| Food       | radish | apricot    | peas | almond-milkmelon    | pepper | potato   | blueberry |

